    <description><![CDATA[<div style="font-size:16px; font-weight:bold; color:black; text-align:left; margin:0px; padding:5px;">Advanced Search Manager for HikaShop installed successfully.</div><div style="font-weight:normal; border-bottom:1px solid #f0dc7e; border-top:1px solid #f0dc7e; display:block; padding:5px; margin:5px; background-color:#fff;">
<img src="components/com_ashs/assets/images/vmloga4.png" style="float:right;margin:0px 15px;width: 400px;"/>

<p style="color:black; font-size:14px;padding-bottom: 12px; text-align:left; margin:0px; padding:5px;">Advanced Search Manager for HikaShop adds search flexibility that you don’t have within either Joomla or HikaShop so as to make you understand your business better , take the guesswork out of what you’re selling, and know more about your customers and the locations where they come from.</p>
<p style="color:black; font-size:14px; padding-bottom: 12px;text-align:left; margin:0px; padding:5px;">Advanced Search Manager for HikaShop will quickly Search, Sort, Save or Export order data. Once a Search query is run, you can review and Sort top level search results, click into specific orders to see complete order and customer detail.</p>

<p style="color:black; font-size:14px;padding-bottom: 12px; text-align:left; margin:0px; padding:5px;">Advanced Search Manager for HikaShop is divided in three parts..</p>

<p style="color:black; font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Search by Order</p>

<ul style="padding-left: 25px;">
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Order Number</p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Order ID</p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Product SKU</p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Product Name</p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Order Status </p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Payment Method</p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Shipping Method</p></li>
</ul>

<p style="color:black; font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; text-align:left; 
 margin:0px; padding:5px;">Search by date</p>
 
<ul style="padding-left: 25px;"> 
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Date range</p></li>
</ul>

<p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Search by Customer</p>

<ul style="padding-left: 25px;">
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">First Name </p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Last Name </p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Email</p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Address </p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">City  </p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">State </p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Country </p></li>
<li><p style="color:black; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; text-align:left;  margin:0px; padding:5px;">Zip </p></li>
</ul>
